OL,3,CITV Wales' General Election Roadshow
OL,4,Cvisits Bridgend: What do voters want?
OL,6,FAs the General Election approaches on
OL,7,F4 July, ITV Cymru Wales has kicked off
OL,8,Fits election roadshow to find out
OL,9,Fexactly what people across Wales want
OL,10,Ffrom a new UK Government.
OL,12,FOur first stop: Bridgend.
OL,14,FLike nearly every constituency in
OL,15,FWales, Bridgend's boundaries are
OL,16,Fchanging, with its edges stretching to
OL,17,Feast Porthcawl.
OL,19,FIn 2019, the constituency turned blue
OL,20,Ffor the first time in 30 years as
OL,21,FJamie Wallis was elected as MP.
