OL,6,F"If the government could lower the
OL,7,Fduty just on commercial premises so to
OL,8,Fencourage more footfall, then there
OL,9,Fwould be a knock-on effect on local
OL,10,Fbusinesses who would sell more food."
OL,12,FAnother told us he wanted to stop
OL,13,Fpaying "so much tax on his pension".
OL,15,F"I've always been one party all my
OL,16,Flife, but I'm beginning to think
OL,17,Fdifferently this year to see who could
OL,18,Foffer me better for my money," he said.
