OL,6,FOne mother who spoke to us wanted
OL,7,Fbetter transparency and clear
OL,8,Fobjectives from the new government, as
OL,9,Fwell as more investment in schools and
OL,10,Feducation.
OL,12,F"I don't think we have a democracy
OL,13,Fanymore and I feel very conflicted
OL,14,Fabout where I will vote, because I
OL,15,Fdon't think any of the parties are
OL,16,Frepresenting the needs of me, my
OL,17,Ffamily, and my wider social group,"
OL,18,Fshe said.
