OL,6,FAnother who spoke to us said money was
OL,7,Fimportant to him when considering who
OL,8,Fto vote for.
OL,10,F"Finances have been stretched
OL,11,Frecently, so I'm interested to see
OL,12,Fwhat will happen depending on who
OL,13,Fwins," he said.
OL,15,F"I'd like whoever is the next prime
OL,16,Fminister to have a meaningful and
OL,17,Frespectful dialogue with Welsh
OL,18,FGovernment. We are one of the devolved
OL,19,Fnations in the UK and I think prime
OL,20,Fministers tend to forget that,"
OL,21,Fanother told ITV Cymru Wales.
