OL,6,FIt means that the Bridgend
OL,7,Fconstituency now looks different to
OL,8,Fhow it did at the last general
OL,9,Felection in 2019.
OL,11,FPart of the former Bridgend
OL,12,Fconstituency has been absorbed into
OL,13,Fthe new constituency of Aberfan
OL,14,FMaesteg, while the new Bridgend
OL,15,Fconstituency joins together parts of
OL,16,Ftwo previous constituencies: Bridgend
OL,17,Fand Ogmore.
OL,19,FThe bulk of the population comes from
OL,20,Fthe former Bridgend seat.
